if the time do not sync

On PC
adb shell "settings put global ntp_server ntp.ntsc.ac.cn"

or On Android
su
settings put global ntp_server ntp.ntsc.ac.cn

then switch use network-provided time off and on to make it work

https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32518769

if usb adb insufficant permission then use adb over wifi
adb connect ip:5555
adb shell "settings put global ntp_server ntp.ntsc.ac.cn"
